(g) The state highway patrol. 22
(2) "Local or state police officer" means any of the 23
following who is under the jurisdiction of the applicable law 24
enforcement official or agency listed in division (A)(1)(a), 25
(b), (c), (d), (e), (f), or (g) of this section that corresponds 26
